{"tid":399163,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"失去人生意義 好想死","createTime":"2017-09-13T17:15:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-14T16:13:02.000Z","uid":146980,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"824840d1de6c72b9dc4bff1afd01365e784ad7a0","tid":399163,"uid":146980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:15:00.000Z","msg":"25歲 不煙不毒不酒<br />\n興趣淨係得打波 其次就係打機同打飛機<br />\n由細到大都好鐘意打波<br />\n由讀書果陣小息lunch放學第一時間衝去打波<br />\n到即使出左黎做野 番工幾攰都好 都唔會放棄呢樣野<br />\n自問打波唔勁 但好鐘意個感覺 好享受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每日番學番工既動力就係之後可以同班fd一齊打波<br />\n可能你地會覺得我咁樣好大細路好唔成熟<br />\n但點都好 打波係我既寄托<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n直到一年前 打波扭親條腰<br />\n本身以為小事 抖幾日就好番 <br />\n點知愈黎愈痛<br />\n睇醫生 再照埋mri 發現係好撚大件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n簡單啲講 就係唔會好番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n時間耐左 日常生活照顧自己開始冇問題<br />\n但想跑快兩步追巴士都唔撚洗指意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n行行企企都還好 條腰有事坐都坐唔撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n坐一陣就痛到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n頹左成年 工都辭埋 好彩既係屋企唔等我養<br />\n日日做廢青 攤係張床到無所事事<br />\n你話咁幾好丫可以抖下 唔打波咪打下機<br />\n冇得長坐 電腦都用唔撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n岩岩得知呢個消息果陣灰到仆街<br />\n女朋友嫌我太消極 走撚埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都岩既 我唔會怪佢<br />\n我都唔想佢同個廢人一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如是者 就咁就廢左一年<br />\n一路都有試過搵唔同興趣/人生目標<br />\n但每樣都玩唔長 始終冇打波果種吸引力<br />\n開始頂唔順 覺得自己搵唔到人生意義<br />\n點解仲要行落去<br />\n<br />\n我生平都冇咩做過啲咩壞事<br />\n最多都係有時睇av睇無碼<br />\n點解個天要咁對我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n借酒消愁愁更愁<br />\n酒我真係唔岩<br />\n飲完醉完第二日又係一樣<br />\n唔知到邊日 我真係再頂唔順<br />\n一跳解千愁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能好多人會覺得冇得打波好少事姐<br />\n大把人成世唔做運動咪又係咁啦<br />\n可能岩既 係我唔知點解咁著緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點都好 多謝你睇晒我發噏風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c1a47706485d9fd90ef597a299b27f98905cae","tid":399163,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:16:28.000Z","msg":"腰痛真係慘"},{"pid":"513680a0cb2c2606bcb74793224ebed7f91ad056","tid":399163,"uid":3167,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:19:10.000Z","msg":"研究下天文同物理啊<br />\n第時可能超越霍金呢"},{"pid":"94c6da43b078d34bb19edcf9d368d2de411dd7c7","tid":399163,"uid":104502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:19:10.000Z","msg":"只可接受<br />\n人生好多野 唔想接受 都要接受"},{"pid":"1d8ab4712b1025afc6346825d869596afd5c82b8","tid":399163,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:22:45.000Z","msg":"踩單車得唔得"},{"pid":"e4c51f28bdf7c1a8921dafa1032880d16e623a22","tid":399163,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:22:57.000Z","msg":"游水都唔得？"},{"pid":"669dd2b38b8f88f2ae924cea7054cbcf7aaebbfb","tid":399163,"uid":146980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:25:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>研究下天文同物理啊<br />\n第時可能超越霍金呢</blockquote><br />\n幾好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0acf4504ba5cc49affc3c811e670a702f4335ec4","tid":399163,"uid":146980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:25:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>踩單車得唔得</blockquote><br />\n唔得 彎腰用力好痛"},{"pid":"246c82a8a9ca7d557b80966568bb38d124ccd7f8","tid":399163,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:26:17.000Z","msg":"點解唔試跌打<br />\n我屋邨附近有個跌打佬口啤唔錯 我自己都睇左好多年 有事就搵佢<br />\n有需要tg vennt44"},{"pid":"9d70b53ac24cf0f47681010d9802291b17847bdc","tid":399163,"uid":146980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:26:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>游水都唔得？</blockquote><br />\n得 但都唔可以用好力 姐係只可以hea游"},{"pid":"bf5add3ec57882c8f6f6e93140df931dff406e69","tid":399163,"uid":146980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:27:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔試跌打<br />\n我屋邨附近有個跌打佬口啤唔錯 我自己都睇左好多年 有事就搵佢<br />\n有需要tg vennt44</blockquote><br />\n有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我個case跌打冇用"},{"pid":"1307b2f351a1de15cbc1ce995ff7a81a1145fdb4","tid":399163,"uid":146980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:27:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>只可接受<br />\n人生好多野 唔想接受 都要接受</blockquote><br />\n接受左一年 就快接受唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b405c0ac45750681d5cd2ca87a2a246079ab03a","tid":399163,"uid":128819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:29:25.000Z","msg":"打咩波,睇波代替得唔得呀,搵隊波支持做精神寄託啦"},{"pid":"a43b122623971369b358567b9489645a1b05a09a","tid":399163,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:29:27.000Z","msg":"強直性脊椎炎？"},{"pid":"81fb33ad726c45595657aa4b34cb3101507b59f4","tid":399163,"uid":82140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:30:24.000Z","msg":"我明你感受<br />\n當人生重要嘅野逐樣逐樣俾人剝奪嘅時候<br />\n真係會對呢個世界覺得好失望，好灰<br />\n幫你唔到<br />\n因為生存嘅動力係要你自己慢慢探索番黎<br />\n只可以講，命運是對手永不低頭"},{"pid":"73b652daef761db1d27841cd5dd4b9f99ddaded1","tid":399163,"uid":146980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:32:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打咩波,睇波代替得唔得呀,搵隊波支持做精神寄託啦</blockquote><br />\n呢個方法幾好 不過始於唔及自己打咁爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19e643f4b15c485227f74d45bca4356090147f0a","tid":399163,"uid":146980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:32:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>強直性脊椎炎？</blockquote><br />\n唔係 但類似"},{"pid":"7b8fa80db04dc175962d790ad43d0901c1ff5ce8","tid":399163,"uid"